Shiramine Shrine is dedicated to deities associated with sports, especially soccer and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kemari" target="_blank">Kemari</a>, an ancient ball game depicted on the <em>ema </em>  (votive plaque) in front of the shrine. Shot on Kodak Ektar 100 film.

</p>
<p class="jp">
白峯神宮の祭神はスポーツ、特にサッカーや<a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/蹴鞠" target="_blank">蹴鞠</a>の神様として親しまれている。正面に掲げられている絵馬には、古代の球技である蹴鞠をする姿が描かれている。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Shrines" /><category term="Film" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Shiramine Shrine is dedicated to deities associated with sports, especially soccer and Kemari, an ancient ball game depicted on the ema (votive plaque) in front of the shrine. Shot on Kodak Ektar 100 film.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2284-positive_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2284-positive_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Nandina・南天</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260118/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Nandina・南天" /><published>2026-01-18T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-18T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nanten</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260118/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
