</p>
<p class="jp">
この南天の赤い実と霜の降りたような緑の葉は、冬を感じさせてくれる。京都府立植物園でコダック ポートラ400フィルムを使って撮影。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Film" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The red berries and frosty green leaves of this Nandina plant really give me the feeling of winter. Taken at the Kyoto Botanical Garden on Kodak Portra 400 film . この南天の赤い実と霜の降りたような緑の葉は、冬を感じさせてくれる。京都府立植物園でコダック ポートラ400フィルムを使って撮影。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2267-positive.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2267-positive.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Katsura River Sunrise・桂川日の出</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260117/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Katsura River Sunrise・桂川日の出" /><published>2026-01-17T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-17T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/katsura</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260117/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Herons and Ducks among the brush on the shallow river at sunrise.
</p>
<p class="jp">
日の出時、浅瀬の茂みにいるサギとカモ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Herons and Ducks among the brush on the shallow river at sunrise. 日の出時、浅瀬の茂みにいるサギとカモ。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_A7R02659.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_A7R02659.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Uchi Lake・内湖</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260116/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Uchi Lake・内湖" /><published>2026-01-16T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-16T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/omi-maiko</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260116/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
