</p>
<p class="jp">
午後の太陽が、平安神宮近くの白川沿いに生えている南天やその他の草木を黄金色に照らしている。</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Higashiyama" /><category term="Rivers" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Film" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The afternoon sun provides a golden light on these Nandina and other brush growing along the Shirakawa river, near Heian Jingu shrine. Shot on Kodak Portra 400 film. 午後の太陽が、平安神宮近くの白川沿いに生えている南天やその他の草木を黄金色に照らしている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2258-positive.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2258-positive.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Senko-ji・千光寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260112/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Senko-ji・千光寺" /><published>2026-01-12T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-12T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/senkoji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260112/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
